sec.p:
This section supplies the details of model specification of the study. Here, the independent variable of Agglomeration economies (AE) is measured using different variables, e.g. Population Growth rate (POG), Number of registered factories (NF), Number of employees working in firms (at all levels) (NE), Housing (percentage of people living in rented houses) (HO), Number of registered motorized vehicles (VEH)10–13,19,31. The details of the variables are provided in Table SI-2.1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
